{"word":"Nob","slug":"nob","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nob</b> <a href=\"#/H5011\">H5011</a> <br/> A city of Benjamin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=32'>Neh 11:32</a><br/> Called &#187;the city of the priests&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=19'>1Sa 22:19</a><br/> Abode of Ahimelech, the priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=1'>1Sa 21:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=11'>1Sa 22:11</a><br/> Probable seat of the tabernacle in Saul's time<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=4'>1Sa 21:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=6'>1Sa 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=9'>1Sa 21:9</a><br/> David flees to, and is aided by Ahimelech<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=9'>1Sa 21:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=10'>1Sa 22:10</a><br/> Destroyed by Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=19'>2Sa 22:19</a><br/> Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=10&verse=32'>Isa 10:32</a>"}]}